:rgba(255, 184, 77, 0.28);background:rgba(255, 184, 77, 0.10);color:var(--warning, #ffb84d);">needs setup</span></div><div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.6;"><div>Linked actions: 1</div><div>Allowed sites: api.example.com</div><div>Allowed folders: /workspace</div><div>Blocked commands: rm rf</div></div></div></div></div><div style="background:var(--bg-secondary);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:16px;"><div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:13px;color:var(--accent);margin-bottom:10px;">Recent Activity</div><div style="padding:10px 0;border-top:none;"><div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:4px;"><div style="color:var(--text-primary);overflow-wrap:anywhere;">exec system</div><span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;border-radius:999px;padding:3px 10px;font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:11px;border:1px solid;border-color:rgba(45, 212, 191, 0.28);background:rgba(45, 212, 191, 0.10);color:var(--teal, #2dd4bf);">allowed</span></div><div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.7;"><div>Who: <span style="color:var(--text-primary);">instance test3</span></div><div>Tool: <span style="color:var(--text-primary);">exec</span></div><div>Applied rules: <span style="color:var(--text-primary);">—, runtime default</span></div><div>Warnings: <span style="color:var(--text-primary);">unbound secret profile</span></div></div></div></div></div>"`;
